casebody.data:
No. 342,

October Term, 1959.

Nostrand et al. v. Little et al., John J. O’Connell, Attorney General of Washington, and Herbert H. Fuller, Chief Assistant Attorney General, for appellees, were on the motion to retax costs. Francis Hoague and Solie Ringold, for appellants, were on the motion to strike.

362 U. S. 474. The motion to strike the motion to retax costs is denied. The motion to retax costs is also denied.
